documents: The Gates of Morning is a short novel by Henry De Vere Stacpoole . The story takes place in the fictional world of the island of Palm Tree, a paradise swarming with devils . The book will be published by John Keirley in September 2015, with the publisher Keirley .

The story of a strange new figure sent by the gods . The island of Palm Tree is described as beautiful as a dream, yet swarming with devils . The novel is called "The Gates Of Morning" and published by Stac Poole at 874-977, published by Simon Tisdall at the University of Oxford .
